The paper deals with image segmentation, specifically for plant root structures. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of fully-connected Conditional Random Fields (CRFs) suggests a machine learning approach, which could also place the paper under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of open source software, which could suggest an emphasis on information retrieval (cs.IR) or multimedia (cs.MM) applications.
